PrecisAmendment to the NATIONAL PARKS CAMPING REGULATIONS increasing some camping fees by an average of 10% and decreasing some by the same to account for changing levels of campground service, bringing some campground fees more in line with local private sector campgrounds and responding to increased camper demand for certain services.

precis:
Amendment to the NATIONAL PARKS CAMPING REGULATIONS increasing some camping
fees by an average of 10% and decreasing some by the same to account for
changing levels of campground service, bringing some campground fees more
in line with local private sector campgrounds and responding to increased
camper demand for certain services.
